et al. (2004), Harada &amp; Yoshida (1978), Harada et al. (1991), Jo Yeong-Seok et al. (2018), Kawai et al. (2003), Lee Jung-Hun (2003), Lee Jung-Hun &amp; Mori (2004), LiuYing, Jin Longru et al. (2009), Luo Jinhong et al. (2012), Maeda (1976), Ohdachi et al. (2009), Ono &amp; Obara (1994), Park Si-Ryong &amp; Won Pyong-Oh (1978), Tiunov (1997), Tsytsulina (2008i), Son Sung-Won et al. (1995), Wang Lei et al. (2014), Xiao Yanhong et al. (2018), Yoo &amp; Yoon Myung-Hee (1992), Yoshiyuki (1989).
